\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {A2}{\ignorespaces Single-parameter sensitivity (tornado chart). $P_{99}\times \theta $ under $G_0$ across the tested range of five parameters. Central value: 2,135. $\alpha $ dominates (319~pts, 15\%); $\mu _{\text  {crisis}}$ is second (162~pts, 8\%); $\eta $, $p_{\text  {crisis}}$, $\beta _{\text  {conform}}$ have small direct effects within tested ranges. \textit  {V5 coupled model, single-parameter variation.}}}{38}{figure.caption.15}\protected@file@percent }
